📚 来源：  
[1] KNOWN: Word loads normal.dotm on startup to initialize VBA environment and UI settings  
[2] MITRE: T1064 (Scripting) — reading normal.dotm alone does not satisfy this technique; requires evidence of code execution from it  
[3] CTI: 15_EmotetCampaign.txt - "it asks them to enable the macros" → implies macro-enabled Word session, which inherently involves normal.dotm access

